177.4]}, {"text": "Erie.", "bbox": [94.9, 1182.0, 138.9, 1204.9]}, {"text": "See the discussion of coal revenues and tonnage, by type of coal, in Part II, Item 7, “Management’s Discussion and", "bbox": [94.9, 1237.0, 1151.4, 1260.0]}, {"text": "Analysis of Financial Condition and Results of Operations.”", "bbox": [94.9, 1264.5, 647.8, 1287.5]}, {"text": "GENERAL MERCHANDISE – Our general merchandise market group is composed of five major commodity", "bbox": [94.9, 1319.6, 1124.8, 1342.6]}, {"text": "groupings:", "bbox": [94.9, 1347.1, 198.8, 1370.0]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [132.4, 1374.6, 140.5, 1397.5]}, {"text": "Chemicals includes sulfur and related chemicals, petroleum products (including crude oil), chlorine and", "bbox": [170.0, 1374.6, 1121.4, 1397.5]}, {"text": "bleaching compounds, plastics, rubber, industrial chemicals, and chemical wastes.", "bbox": [170.0, 1402.1, 933.9, 1425.0]}, {"text": "•", "bbox": [132.4, 1429.6, 140.5, 1452.5]}, {"text": "Agriculture, consumer products, and government includes soybeans, wheat, corn, fertilizer, livestock and", "bbox": [170.0, 1429.6, 1133.8, 1452.5]}, {"text": "poultry feed, food oils, flour, beverages, canned goods, sweeteners, consumer products, ethanol,", "bbox": [170.0, 1457.1, 1051.0, 1480.1]}, {"text": "transportation equipment, and items for the U.S. military.", "bbox": [170.0, 1484.6, 706.7, 1507.6]}, {"text": "K5", "bbox": [614.6, 1576.1, 642.6, 1599.1]}]}